1
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:21,060
♪Take a guess♪

2
00:00:21,180 --> 00:00:25,100
♪Guess who pretends to care♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:29,460
♪Who's playing nice♪

4
00:00:29,740 --> 00:00:36,060
♪What my next line will be♪

5
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:38,380
♪Take a guess♪

6
00:00:38,380 --> 00:00:42,740
♪Like a hunter lying in wait♪

7
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:46,860
♪With the posture of prey♪

8
00:00:47,220 --> 00:00:53,500
♪Is this kiss for goodbye or love?♪

9
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:56,060
♪Take a guess♪

10
00:00:56,060 --> 00:01:00,060
♪She fell from grace♪

11
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:04,220
♪Is it a trap or an accident?♪

12
00:01:04,660 --> 00:01:09,100
♪Or your future?♪

13
00:01:10,900 --> 00:01:13,140
♪Take a guess♪

14
00:01:13,460 --> 00:01:17,260
♪I set the stage♪

15
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:21,620
♪Is it pain or pleasure?♪

16
00:01:21,980 --> 00:01:26,700
♪Applaud the show♪

17
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:32,260
♪Can you see the smile or not?♪

18
00:01:32,260 --> 00:01:36,660
♪Can you tell if it's a lie or truth?♪

19
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:41,020
♪Will you toss and turn at night?♪

20
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:43,180
♪Should you guess like this?♪

21
00:01:43,180 --> 00:01:45,380
[We All Lie]

22
00:01:45,380 --> 00:01:49,060
[Episode 4]

23
00:01:49,490 --> 00:01:51,120
[Episode 4]
Of course it's fake news.

24
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:54,020
[Exposed to the Sun]
Shuheng's with his wife right now.

25
00:01:54,290 --> 00:01:55,120
They're such a loving couple.

26
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,620
How could he possibly cheat on her?

27
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,320
Yeah,

28
00:01:58,460 --> 00:02:00,460
it must be someone who tries
to tarnish our reputation.

29
00:02:01,690 --> 00:02:03,820
So you have to clarify it in your report,
Mr. Wang.

30
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:05,360
Okay.

31
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:10,620
I must say, you're really...

32
00:02:16,220 --> 00:02:17,460
Hello, Mr. Zhang?

33
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,460
That guy's outrageous.

34
00:02:19,690 --> 00:02:20,760
Took the money and still broke the news,

35
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,620
treating us like fools.

36
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,360
What a terrible loss.

37
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:27,960
The priority is
to solve the problem we face now.

38
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,820
But later I'll find this person

39
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,320
and make him cough up our money,

40
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:33,520
before giving him a good beating.

41
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:35,290
Okay, I see.

42
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:42,060
I just contacted some companies
that own hundreds of marketing accounts,

43
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:43,720
but none of them agree to take
our publicity job.

44
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:45,660
Why? Don't they want to make money?

45
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,260
There's only one possibility.

46
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:49,690
They must have taken our opponents' offer
to create trending topics.

47
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,160
Who on earth is it?

48
00:02:52,290 --> 00:02:53,290
Who have you offended recently?

49
00:02:54,290 --> 00:02:55,720
I've offended nobody.

50
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:01,890
A call from the director.

51
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:08,020
Director?

52
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,900
I know.

53
00:03:11,420 --> 00:03:13,090
Yes, I'm really sorry, Director.

54
00:03:16,290 --> 00:03:18,020
Shuheng? OK.

55
00:03:26,060 --> 00:03:26,820
Director.

56
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:28,290
What's really going on with you all?

57
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:30,220
We're a few days away from the filming.

58
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:31,720
You've created such a big scandal.

59
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,160
How am I supposed to say to the investors?

60
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:34,660
You have two days.

61
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:36,860
If you can't settle this scandal,

62
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:37,760
consider it a breach of contract.

63
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:40,160
You and Chen Yingying should be ready
to pay out of your pocket.

64
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:48,360
Ganggang, get in touch
with more marketing accounts,

65
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,420
ask them to delete the negative comments.

66
00:03:50,090 --> 00:03:50,460
Okay.

67
00:03:57,020 --> 00:04:00,420
[Su Li]

68
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:03,220
[Ganggang]

69
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,760
[Su Li, you finally show up.]
Hello.

70
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,320
[I've been your fan for long.]

71
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:50,090
[Finally, I get to meet the real person.]
Hello, everyone. I'm Su Li.

72
00:04:50,090 --> 00:04:51,020
[I love the play you wrote!]
Welcome joining me

73
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:52,490
[When will the next play be released?]
in today's live room.

74
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,220
[Su Li, you're both pretty and talented.]
Today,

75
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,660
[Su Li, I love you so much!]
I want to share

76
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:58,760
[Like you a lot.]
with you some books I usually read,

77
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,920
[I envy your talent and good look.]
the ones I really like.

78
00:05:01,090 --> 00:05:02,500
What I'm going to share are two fictions

79
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:05,420
by Edgar Allen Poe.

80
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:07,560
One is The Murders in the Rue Morgue,

81
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:10,490
and the other one is The Gold-Bug.

82
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:13,560
Why do I choose to share these two?

83
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:18,060
It's because my husband bought them
for me recently.

84
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:18,940
[Su Li, I like you so much.]

85
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,960
[Everyone, check your Weibo.]
My husband really likes preparing

86
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:24,560
[There's juicy gossip on Weibo.]
little gifts and surprises for me,

87
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:27,520
but sometimes it makes me nervous.

88
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:29,420
I start wondering if I forgot

89
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:31,740
some important anniversary or something.

90
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,660
Ganggang, step out for a second.

91
00:05:36,060 --> 00:05:36,600
Okay.

92
00:05:45,660 --> 00:05:48,530
Shuheng, call Su Li right now.

93
00:05:50,060 --> 00:05:52,200
Withdrawing the trending topics is
the top priority.

94
00:05:52,530 --> 00:05:53,530
Explain to her later.

95
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:56,460
Only Su Li can help salvage your image,

96
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:57,860
and get rid of the scandal now.

97
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,460
Although public opinion is one-sided now,

98
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:03,700
if Su Li can step forward
and help us clarify

99
00:06:04,660 --> 00:06:05,730
that we were just reading a script

100
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,660
and she'd also be present,

101
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,760
even going as far as to say
it was a script meeting she organized,

102
00:06:13,730 --> 00:06:16,130
the few remaining nitpickers won't be able
to do anything.

103
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,160
That's right.

104
00:06:19,820 --> 00:06:20,490
It makes sense.

105
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:22,920
But why would Su Li help us?

106
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,920
She's no fool,

107
00:06:24,290 --> 00:06:26,060
she wouldn't believe
we were simply reading the script.

108
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:27,690
She's no fool.

109
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,220
If she's no fool,

110
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:32,820
how could we have kept her
in the dark for so long

111
00:06:32,820 --> 00:06:34,020
and she still knows nothing?

112
00:06:35,660 --> 00:06:37,460
When a woman falls in love,

113
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:39,420
she turns blind, deaf and fool.

114
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:46,120
One of the top four female mystery writers
was Josephine Tey.

115
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:48,860
The Daughter of Time by her is

116
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:51,960
the most famous historical mystery.

117
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,920
(Su Li, are you okay?)

118
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,690
(Su Li, are the trending topics real?)

119
00:06:55,690 --> 00:06:57,160
(Where's your husband?)

120
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,860
(Are all the revelations true?)

121
00:07:02,820 --> 00:07:04,620
Am I okay?

122
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,090
[Su Li, are the trending topics real?]
I'm good.

123
00:07:07,090 --> 00:07:08,220
[Are all the revelations true?]

124
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:10,360
[Check out what's trending!]
My husband's doing his hair and makeup.

125
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,520
His new play is about to start filming?

126
00:07:13,420 --> 00:07:15,160
(Su Li, you got to check what's trending.)

127
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:16,820
(Your husband's cheating.)

128
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:21,090
My husband's cheating?

129
00:07:21,090 --> 00:07:23,290
(Su Li, go to check out what's trending!)

130
00:07:25,620 --> 00:07:26,920
Alright, I'll take a look.

131
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:29,180
[Zhang Shuheng and Chen Yingying
at Ruijing Hotel,]

132
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:30,540
[suspected of soliciting,
under police investigation.]

133
00:07:30,540 --> 00:07:31,740
[Famous screenwriter Su Li's husband
and Chen Yingying]

134
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:32,940
[were arrested by the police at the hotel,
suspected of cheating.]

135
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:37,560
[Zhang Shuheng, you shameless!]

136
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,260
[This bastard doesn't deserve you.]

137
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:38,900
[I feel so sorry for you, Su Li.]

138
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,220
(Jerk gets out
of the entertainment industry.)

139
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:43,090
(This jerk doesn't deserve you.)

140
00:07:43,090 --> 00:07:45,890
(Su Li, you're talented and beautiful.
Ditch the jerk.)

141
00:07:45,890 --> 00:07:48,120
(The kept man only got famous
because of you,)

142
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,560
(he has the nerve to cheat?)

143
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:52,020
[Seriously, it's not worth it.]
No...

144
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,560
[Don't cry, Su Li]
This photo...

145
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,420
[I have a friend working
in the public security bureau.]

146
00:07:56,420 --> 00:07:58,860
[He said he saw it with his own eyes.]
This photo is doctored, right?

147
00:07:58,860 --> 00:08:01,290
(I have a friend who works at the hotel,)

148
00:08:01,290 --> 00:08:03,460
(saying that they got a report
of soliciting.)

149
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:05,920
(Went to bust the hotel
and it turned out to be them.)

150
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:09,020
(What's more, they were caught in bed.)

151
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:12,890
(Su Li, someone proved on Weibo,
saying he just lived next door.)

152
00:08:12,890 --> 00:08:15,360
(He saw them taken away by the police,)

153
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,960
(both looking disheveled.)

154
00:08:18,820 --> 00:08:21,860
[Caught on bed! Can't be whitewashed.]
Is...is this possible?

155
00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:23,340
[People like him should be put into prison
and stop wreaking havoc.]

156
00:08:24,060 --> 00:08:25,520
Excuse me.

157
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:51,090
(Su Li, don't let this couple
of jerks ruin your mood.)

158
00:08:51,090 --> 00:08:53,260
(Zhang Shuheng really sucks!)

159
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:54,660
(He got famous because of you,)

160
00:08:54,660 --> 00:08:56,060
(now he does this.)

161
00:08:56,060 --> 00:08:57,060
(Chen Yingying as well.)

162
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:59,290
(She doesn't deserve your kindness.)

163
00:08:59,290 --> 00:09:00,690
(Feel for you, Su Li.)

164
00:09:00,690 --> 00:09:02,160
(Don't cry, Su Li.)

165
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:04,020
(That jerk doesn't deserve it.)

166
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:08,560
(You're so nice.
That couple of jerks will rot in hell.)

167
00:09:19,860 --> 00:09:21,660
How about now? Still not picking up?

168
00:09:22,420 --> 00:09:23,490
She's not answering calls,

169
00:09:23,490 --> 00:09:24,660
nor Wechat message.

170
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,090
She's probably asleep.

171
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:30,920
Boss, a topic suddenly appears
and becomes the second trending one,

172
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:32,690
saying that Su Li saw the news
of your affair

173
00:09:32,690 --> 00:09:35,020
during her live stream
and burst into tears.

174
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:42,490
After watching the live stream,
many people are posting to criticize us.

175
00:09:42,490 --> 00:09:44,090
Loads of fans unfollowed
and turned their back against us.

176
00:09:44,090 --> 00:09:46,460
Our fan pages and the topic center
are flooded with negative messages.

177
00:09:46,460 --> 00:09:48,020
There's nothing but insults.

178
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:48,720
Besides,

179
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,260
the official Weibo account
for the new play is filled

180
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:52,490
with comments demanding changing
leading actor and actress.

181
00:09:56,660 --> 00:09:57,760
It's over.

182
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:00,220
Everything is ruined.

183
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:31,490
Honey, I...

184
00:10:32,060 --> 00:10:33,120
I trust you.

185
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:37,860
I said,

186
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:40,960
I believe there's nothing between you two.

187
00:10:41,460 --> 00:10:44,520
These picture-based news stories
are completely untrustworthy.

188
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,860
One's my husband.

189
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:48,890
One's my bestie.

190
00:10:49,820 --> 00:10:53,460
You are the people closest to me
in this world.

191
00:10:55,660 --> 00:10:57,090
You don't need to explain.

192
00:10:58,260 --> 00:10:59,690
I won't believe

193
00:10:59,690 --> 00:11:02,160
that you could engage in such despicable,

194
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:04,090
sordid affairs, no better than animals.

195
00:11:06,420 --> 00:11:09,120
Even if someone tried
to seduce my husband,

196
00:11:09,820 --> 00:11:11,760
I also believe

197
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:13,860
that Shuheng will know what to do.

198
00:11:16,220 --> 00:11:18,220
This whole thing is clearly someone trying

199
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:20,320
to set up a scheme,

200
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:22,260
aiming to frame and take over.

201
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,690
Yingying, do you think I'm right?

202
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:26,690
Su Li, this's really a misunderstanding.

203
00:11:27,660 --> 00:11:29,320
Yeah, Honey.

204
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:33,060
I think it's very odd.

205
00:11:33,060 --> 00:11:35,120
You see, we had a drink that night.

206
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,690
You were drunk and fell asleep.

207
00:11:36,690 --> 00:11:38,980
As it happened, I was asked
for a script reading meeting.

208
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:40,820
Yingying and I arrived there early,

209
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,720
then the police came shortly after.

210
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:47,260
Honey, I'm worried you'll believe

211
00:11:47,260 --> 00:11:49,260
those malicious comments online
with hidden motives.

212
00:11:50,490 --> 00:11:51,520
I'm so touched

213
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:52,760
that you still trust me.

214
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:57,660
What a great wife.

215
00:11:57,660 --> 00:12:01,260
Shuheng, you have to be nice to Su Li.
Do you hear me?

216
00:12:01,260 --> 00:12:02,260
That's for sure.

217
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:06,360
Then the top priority now is

218
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:08,760
holding a press conference
as soon as possible.

219
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:10,890
You three clarify to the public

220
00:12:10,890 --> 00:12:11,820
that it's a misunderstanding.

221
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:17,860
I agree,

222
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:21,520
but it's a temporary solution.

223
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:23,220
What I worry now is,

224
00:12:23,220 --> 00:12:24,860
if Shuheng and Yingying

225
00:12:24,860 --> 00:12:27,960
show up together in public
like they used to,

226
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:30,960
it will agitate
the irrational internet users.

227
00:12:31,290 --> 00:12:31,890
How about this?

228
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:35,560
Shuheng, Yingying, I'm going to cancel

229
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,060
all your upcoming jobs for now.

230
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:39,260
I'll put a hold on all your current jobs,

231
00:12:39,260 --> 00:12:40,490
including the new teleplay.

232
00:12:41,090 --> 00:12:42,720
Once this scandal is over

233
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,180
and the public forgets about it,

234
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:45,780
it won't be late for you two to come back.

235
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,100
No.

236
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,660
I can compromise on anything

237
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:49,660
but the teleplay.

238
00:12:50,930 --> 00:12:51,730
Su Li,

239
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:53,700
you got to trust me.

240
00:12:54,260 --> 00:12:55,760
Don't panic, Yingying.

241
00:12:56,700 --> 00:12:58,130
Given the current situation,

242
00:12:58,130 --> 00:13:00,060
even if I step in to clarify for you,

243
00:13:00,060 --> 00:13:02,160
do you really think the public is going
to accept actors like you two

244
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:04,330
who've stirred up such a scandal

245
00:13:04,330 --> 00:13:05,800
to be in the same play?

246
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,760
For the big picture

247
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:10,500
and the long-term development
of both your careers,

248
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:11,900
I think

249
00:13:12,900 --> 00:13:15,100
this is the best solution.

250
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:15,930
I agree.

251
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,130
Me too.

252
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,000
Honey, we're running out of time.

253
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:27,530
We should hurry up and think
about what to say at the press conference.

254
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,200
What's up?

255
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:51,130
Don't you find this whole thing fishy?

256
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:54,460
We happened to encounter a police check
at the hotel.

257
00:13:54,660 --> 00:13:55,800
Now with our new play's filming
about to start,

258
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:57,730
this information just happened
to get exposed.

259
00:13:58,130 --> 00:13:58,600
Plus,

260
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,660
Su Li almost never livestreams,

261
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:02,400
yet did it right at this critical time.

262
00:14:03,560 --> 00:14:04,560
I strongly suspect

263
00:14:05,130 --> 00:14:06,900
she deliberately cried
