401
00:22:21,800 --> 00:22:24,760
I also hope that all my fans

402
00:22:25,260 --> 00:22:26,700
and the press can give me a second chance.

403
00:22:28,300 --> 00:22:28,930
Thank you.

404
00:22:37,460 --> 00:22:39,330
What's your comment on this, Ms. Su Li?

405
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:53,930
This's indeed a misunderstanding.

406
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,960
I know about the script reading meeting.

407
00:22:57,000 --> 00:23:00,730
I absolutely believe there's nothing
between Shuheng and my bestie, Yingying.

408
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:07,660
